metadata.name: OG Cake Lover
metadata.description:
I made this open edition to celebrate my birthday and first year in the nft space.  
Collectors of this cake will be considered OG Cake Lovers.  
I always wanted to thank those who believed in me since the beginning and give them the chance to have special benefits.  
Holders will have pre-sale on all my future artworks and projects, discounts on particular drops, gifts, raffles and much more  
(all my old collectors are getting this nft as an airdrop)
